      "comment": "ASCEND JACARANDA (4) missed the hat-trick last start when fourth and beaten 11 lengths (30.52) last time at The Meadows. Form here sound including eight wins. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Looks the one to beat on her best form. LANDED (2) missed the frame last time at Wagga but the start prior rocketed around 425m at Bendigo in 23.79. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. PAW LILIBET (3) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 5 lengths at Goulburn in a handy 19.70 beating Made By Mia. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. One of the leading chances again. ARCTIC IMAGE (1) is a last-start placegetter worth considering.",
